title: @OspreyWSOC plays Kennesaw State, USC Upstate in A-Sun Road Weekend
text: 5' 9" Fr. JACKSONVILLE, Fla. â€“ The North Florida Women's Soccer team continues Atlantic Sun Conference play, facing Kennesaw State Friday at 2 p.m. and USC Upstate Sunday at 1 p.m. on the road. The Ospreys (4-9-0, 2-2-0 A-Sun) currently sit in fourth place in the conference standings with three matches remaining in the regular season. Kennesaw State (4-8-2, 1-2-1 A-Sun) is tied for fifth, while USC Upstate (2-11-1, 1-3-0 A-Sun) sits in seventh place.
